ITERATOR 1.0.0
--------------

	andrew.international@gmail.com
	April 2012

Iterated Function System [1] [2] Explorer.

Program requirements:
 - Java 1.6.0 Runtime Environment
 - Windows, Linux or OSX Operating System

Run the program as follows, with the '-F' option to specify full-screen,
using the relevant script for your operating system..

    $ ./bin/explorer.sh [-F]
    $ ./bin/explorer.command [-F]
    c> .\bin\explorer.cmd [-F]

